name: Pinwheel Ice Cream Note Card Set
description:
Spumoni Anyone?

From Inkspot Workshop's Pinwheel
collection is a set of 10 scrumptous, 
folded ice cream cone notecards with
coordinating envelopes. Each set 
is bound with our paper and ribbon band, 
then packaged in a clear, resealable, 
cellophane envelope. 

Notecards:
- Original Inkspot Workshop Design
- 10 blank, top folded, stylish rounded corners
- Bright white linen 80# cover stock
- 4.25 x 5.5 inches folded
- Digitally printed using high quality ink
- May be personalized for .25 each card

Envelopes:
- 10 your choice of color, chocolate, lime
or raspberry, or mix and match.

Thank you for looking!

name: Jax Pink and Green Note Card Set
description:
Doesn't this pattern just make you feel
like a kid again? 

Set of 10 fun, pink, green and tiffany blue
folded notecards and coordinating envelopes. 
Each set is bound with our paper and ribbon band, 
then packaged in a clear, resealable, cellophane 
envelope. 

Notecards:
- Original Inkspot Workshop Design
- 10 blank on the inside, stylish rounded corners
- 110# heavy, bright white, smooth card stock
- 4.25 x 5.5 inches folded
- Printed on front and back

Envelopes:
- 10 European Pointed Flap, your choice of color,
pool blue or chocolate.

If you would like more than 10, just let me know. 

Thank you for looking!

name: Chandelier Thank You Cards
description:
From Inkspot Workshop is a set of
12 folded chandelier - thank you - 
notecards, printed in rich chocolate
ink. Try them personalized! Come
with brown, european point flap
envelopes. Each set is bound with our 
paper and ribbon band, then packaged in 
a clear, resealable, cellophane envelope. 

Notecards:
- 12 blank, top folded, stylish rounded corners
- Heavy duty colored card stock
- 5.5 w x 4.25 h inches folded
- Digitally printed using high quality ink
- 4 of each color and chandelier style, unless 
you would like all one color and one chandelier style.

If you wish to have this set in just one color or personalized, please specify any changes in the notes to seller

Thank you for looking!
